{"tid":432106,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"配音太認真！小埋聲優拒用音效「吃麵配音」　日網興奮：啪啪聲呢？","createTime":"2017-10-11T08:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T13:10:54.000Z","uid":51904,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0574b20217c1961e80c2861ad27b151eeba39032","tid":432106,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"日本聲優有多厲害？能變換不同情緒、角色、性別是基本功，要一人分飾多角也不甚麼難事，但許多人不知道的是，除了人物對話以外，有時候動畫裡的聲音特效也是聲優親自配出來的。<br />\n<br />\n近期在2CH上就瘋傳一張聲優配音照，動畫《干物妹！小埋》吃麵時的配音原來是這樣配出來的：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2851/2851483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2851%2F2851483.jpg&h=89f4d7f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2851/2851481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2851%2F2851481.jpg&h=cbd1d088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不用罐頭音效，為了追求配音的帶入感與逼真感，聲優不曉得吃了多少碗麵，重複錄了幾次。許多2CH鄉民紛紛表示：<br />\n<br />\n「很臭的樣子。」<br />\n<br />\n「好專業，難道啪啪的聲音也是&hellip;？」<br />\n<br />\n「洗澡的時候，聲優也要敬業洗澡一下吧？」<br />\n<br />\n「真可憐，這碗是便宜貨，很大碗卻超難吃。」<br />\n<br />\n「據說H動畫與遊戲的口交配音是真的口交」<br />\n<br />\n「樓上講的是真的，只不過是吸手指頭。」<br />\n<br />\n看到這邊，胖丁覺得很驚訝阿，沒想到動畫的奇怪音效還是聲優自己配出來的，難怪日本人把聲優捧的這麼高，因為在動畫中，他們簡直就是另一種境界的演員了阿嗚嗚～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vojipKG9hUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvojipKG9hUU&d=b49nBMzqX%2FccfoyRtTDYMaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=0ab74dee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vojipKG9hUU</a>"},{"pid":"f7d70b53d2b478b68ef1227b4f4a3978ccf380d0","tid":432106,"uid":48277,"like":8,"dislike":17,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"小埋係雞係公廁"},{"pid":"bf800e2ec058b0f2d790a51d68c348e6d0176681","tid":432106,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:11:46.000Z","msg":"敬業好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7caf2868b1cde79a57d412ab1dcb35aae5387a4","tid":432106,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:16:08.000Z","msg":"田中正喔"},{"pid":"c24a512d1fc6848ae7a33e4cb672851dbe754c5a","tid":432106,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"H-ACG同音聲啲SFX/SE係會俾人屌似食麵聲(真係用 &quot;noddle-slurping sound&quot;)"},{"pid":"52d5ab40b9161b04824fc21fa18d058c9a3613b9","tid":432106,"uid":35420,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"段片又係個啲 幾張圖加 堆字當係片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92df2b790036128ba9208fc714949cc61ef9706","tid":432106,"uid":8307,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:58:06.000Z","msg":"配音員終於可以邊食飯邊工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9fe8d3296d6050951eacbe4de4f22f2b21a21c","tid":432106,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>配音員終於可以邊食飯邊工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 異世界食堂之類<br />\n<br />\n咪可以一路大餐一路配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030f18e46535f1b45685a8a17fc437f102d63dfe","tid":432106,"uid":7307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>配音員終於可以邊食飯邊工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma